{"title":"短歌四首","authors":["峭岩"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"短歌四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风把它吹落这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只给它一张石床"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面陡壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个缝隙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它顽强地奋争了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根，深深扎下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕曲折"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕艰巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它终于站稳脚跟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍峨耸立在石崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招满天雄风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤秋夏风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不失时机地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人类献上一抹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀削的石峰犬牙之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耸立着一棵棵生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一幅天然壁画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执意在悬崖上描绘风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些树辞掉一切丰厚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽强地固守恬淡和贫瘠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可张开苍老的枝干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽力吸收阳光的普照山泉的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最小的获取最大的回报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夏有红，秋冬有绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们从此看到生命的伟大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也不会在困苦面前叹息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们做一棵会呼唤的树吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对生活永远充满希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要把根深深扎进土壤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会迎来如花似锦的四季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近三塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄走近你，三塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是晨曦初照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天微霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光涂满你的胴体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流光溢彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秀水映亮你的古老又年轻的面颊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三姊妹站在那里就是历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨幕拉开就是一幅惊世的画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步轻轻，不忍踏破你的静美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿翼翼，唯恐添一份嘈杂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄走近你，三塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近历史的深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近昨天的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近苍山洱海的传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近白族人民创世的神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外婆桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是外婆桥吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上垒砌的故事  被水孵化出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个细节一支支插曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥东  演化着集市的繁荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥西  品味着生活的甜美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外婆不在了乘水流东去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没带走一丝如意的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的歌谣留在桥上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在月下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人们划船去打捞……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}